attributes = objects.Attributes(attributes=[primitives.Enumeration(enums.
    ObjectType, value=enums.ObjectType.PUBLIC_KEY, tag=enums.Tags.
    OBJECT_TYPE)], tag=enums.Tags.PUBLIC_KEY_ATTRIBUTES)
value = objects.convert_attributes_to_template_attribute(attributes)
self.assertIsInstance(value, objects.TemplateAttribute)
self.assertEqual(value.tag, enums.Tags.PUBLIC_KEY_TEMPLATE_ATTRIBUTE)
self.assertIsInstance(value.attributes, list)
self.assertEqual(1, len(value.attributes))
self.assertIsInstance(value.attributes[0], objects.Attribute)
self.assertEqual('Object Type', value.attributes[0].attribute_name.value)
self.assertEqual(primitives.Enumeration(enums.ObjectType, value=enums.
    ObjectType.PUBLIC_KEY, tag=enums.Tags.ATTRIBUTE_VALUE), value.
    attributes[0].attribute_value)
